    "The sigmadelta neurons [34] leverage the high ReLU similarity between consecutive video frames to produce high activation (message) sparsity on-chip.",
    "Second, S5, a state space model [47] adapted for activation sparsity on Loihi 2 by adding ReLU activations [38], applied to an audio denoising task [54].",
    "To avoid I/O latency bottlenecks [46], we study accelerator performance using input data loaded into neurocores on chip.",
